# Chrome bookmarks

Chrome bookmarks is a Chrome browser application, which allows you to:

- Do advanced search on your bookmarks by tags, url or title.
- Add custom tags for bookmarks, which helps you to manage all your bookmarks. By default application uses folders as tags for bookmarks.

